SUMMARY: A Norfolk Southern conductor trainee was killed on the job this week in Bessemer, Alabama, when a piece of metal from a passing train car crashed into the victim's cab

TITLE: Self-driving truck company TuSimple to lay off hundreds days before Christmas: report
